  "subject": "Create cm handle from NCMP Inventory returns Server Error caused by LogFormatUtils error",
  "commit_message": "Create cm handle from NCMP Inventory returns Server Error caused by LogFormatUtils error\n\n- An older version of Spring being pulled in as a transitive dependency of another library\n  that was causing NoSuchMethodError:  org.springframework.core.log.LogFormatUtils.formatValue(...).\n- Added bill of materials feature to solve just such issues. (Introduced into Spring 4).\n- Removed the <version/> element from all possible spring libraries declared in our POM.\n- Test is updated to cover AlreadyDefinedException. (http status 409)\n\nIssue-ID: CPS-927\nSigned-off-by: sourabh_sourabh <sourabh.sourabh@est.tech>\nChange-Id: I48e21697f629b530e62d7bd6c1f2914115531928\n",
